<plot>A young woman wakes up, hung-over and bleary-eyed, and tries to piece together what it is she got up to the night before. Through a series of flashbacks we watch the evening unfold in a haze of drunken calls, as she toys with potential lovers over games of chess and KerPlunk. Her smitten ex boyfriend narrates the story of a night she will come to regret.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?577449</url></doc>
